# TDD REFACTOR PHASE SKILL

## Goal
Improve code structure without changing behavior.

## Input
- Passing production code
- Passing tests

## Output
- Same behavior
- Improved internal structure

## Rules
- Do NOT modify tests
- Do NOT change observable behavior
- Only structural improvements allowed
- Changes must be small and incremental

## Constraints
- All tests must remain passing at all times
- Refactor must not introduce new behavior